headline: Putnam Greene Financial Corporation Chooses Jack Henry to Improve Operations Across Four Banks
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today that Putnam Greene Financial Corporation, a Georgia-based bank holding company, has selected Jack Henry to modernize its technology infrastructure, standardize operations, and enhance digital experiences across its four subsidiary banks.
